(366, 208, 'content', '<strong><u>Beetroot Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Packed with the goodness of Beetroot, it has great moisturizing and skin healing properties.</li>\r\n 	<li>Effective in reducing blemishes and dark spots, removing tan and lightening the skin tone.</li>\r\n 	<li>Helps in preventing premature ageing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong><u>Contains</u></strong> : Beetroot puree, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong><u>Suitable for</u></strong> : All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong><u>Available in</u></strong>: 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-210 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Beetroot-Soap2-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"353\" />'),
