(379, 212, 'content', '<strong><u>Aloe Vera Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Has great moisturizing effect.</li>\r\n 	<li>Relieves dry skin, irritation, itching and promotes skin healing.</li>\r\n 	<li>Aloe Vera has anti bacterial properties.</li>\r\n 	<li>Treats sunburns and lightens skin tan.</li>\r\n 	<li>For men, its healing properties can heal small cuts caused by shaving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Aloe Vera, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\nSuitable for: All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage:</strong>Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-214 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aloe-Vera-Soap3-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"355\" />'),
