(387, 215, 'content', '<strong><u>Besan - Turmeric Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Has great tan removing effect.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleanses, exfoliates and brightens skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Turmeric has antibacterial and antioxidant properties, which helps in reducing acne.</li>\r\n 	<li>Reduces oiliness.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lightens acne marks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Besan, Turmeric, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E.\r\nProduct is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><u><img class=\" wp-image-220 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Besan-Turmeric-Soap-compressed-11zon-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"354\" /></u></strong>'),
