(416, 225, 'excerpt', '<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Enjoy this moisturizing soap which is full of antioxidants &amp; soothing benefits. Include carrot soap in your daily beauty regimen for a healthy and clearer skin.</span>'),
(417, 225, 'content', '<strong><u>Carrot Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Rich in anti oxidant Beta Carotene, this soap helps in rejuvenating and restoring the skin, making it smooth and supple.</li>\r\n 	<li>Helps to slow down skinâs aging.</li>\r\n 	<li>Reduces tan, skin blemishes and gives a radiant appearance. Evens out your skin tone.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heals and protects skin from the damage caused by UV rays and environmental pollution.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gently removes dirt and oil without stripping your skin of its vital moisture.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Carrot extract, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in</strong>: 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<strong>Â </strong><img class=\" wp-image-227 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Carrot-Soap-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"355\" />'),
