(423, 228, 'excerpt', '<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Charcoal soap is best for oily skin; brings an oil balance, especially the facial skin and gives a clear oil-free look. It absorbs the excess oil and helps to remove dirt from the skin.</span>'),
(424, 228, 'content', '<strong><u>Charcoal Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Good for oily skin, makes skin tighter and firmer.</li>\r\n 	<li>Prevents premature aging and good for acne and psoriasis.</li>\r\n 	<li>Extracts the dirt and grime from clogged pores and reduces their size.</li>\r\n 	<li>Especially beneficial for people living in cities for whom itâs important to remove daily pollutants.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides a gentle, natural exfoliation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Charcoal, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> Oily Skin.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-229 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Charcoal-Soap-compressed-11zon-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"355\" />'),
