(436, 231, 'excerpt', '<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">An amazing gift for yourself and to that special someone so they remember you when they shower.Â  Hearts embedded into lovely hydrating rosewater soap.Â  It\'s great fun.</span>'),
(437, 231, 'content', '<strong><u>Embedded Soap</u></strong>\r\n\r\nThe rose water in the soap helps in maintaining the pH balance of the skin and controls excess oil. It hydrates, cleans and regenerates tissues and gives a glowing skin\r\n\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Rose Water, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E.\r\nProduct is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<strong>Â </strong><img class=\" wp-image-232 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Embeded-Soap-300x204.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"363\" />'),
