(450, 234, 'content', '<strong><u>Kasthuri Manjal Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Helps in reducing acne marks, brightens and rejuvenates skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heals skin infection and insect bites.</li>\r\n 	<li>Fights pimples and provides a youthful glow to your skin</li>\r\n 	<li>Highly effective for removing suntan.</li>\r\n 	<li>Slows down aging and wrinkle formation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Kasturi Manjal (pure wild turmeric), Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E.\r\nProduct is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-235 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kasturi-Manjal-compressed-11zon-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"355\" />'),
