(480, 246, 'content', '<strong><u>Neem &amp; Tulsi Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Has great moisturizing effect.</li>\r\n 	<li>Has anti bacterial and anti fungal properties.</li>\r\n 	<li>Good for minor skin irritation and acne.</li>\r\n 	<li>Controls excess oil and restores skinâs moisture.</li>\r\n 	<li>For men, its healing properties can heal small cuts caused by shaving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Fresh Neem &amp; Tulsi extracts, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E.\r\nProduct is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage:Â </strong> * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-247 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Neem-Tulsi-Soap-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"355\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Â </strong>'),
