(490, 249, 'content', '<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Oatmeal Soap</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Oatmeal is rich in anti-oxidants and is great for treating skin problems, such as itching, eczema and psoriasis.</li>\r\n 	<li>Contains natural ingredients which aid in removing the dead skin cells gently.</li>\r\n 	<li>Helps lessen the oil secretion of your skin without drying and making it uncomfortable.</li>\r\n 	<li>The healing properties found in oatmeal heal sunburns and acts as a barrier to the sun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Effective for dark circles under your eyes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Balances skinâs pH, moisturizes and enhances the skin tone, making it glow.</li>\r\n 	<li>Has a great cleansing property because of the chemical saponin in oatmeal.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\nContains : Goatmilk, Oatmeal, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\nSuitable for: All skin types, especially those with sensitive skin.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\nAvailable in: 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-251 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Oatmeal-Soap-compressed-11zon-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"353\" />'),
