(500, 252, 'content', '<strong><u>Orange Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Removes dirt / impurities and reduces tan.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nourishes and restores the suppleness of your skin and keeps it moisturized.</li>\r\n 	<li>Full of antiseptic and antibacterial properties.</li>\r\n 	<li>It helps to maintain a clear skin tone.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Orange extract and zest, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-254 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Orange-Soap-compressed-11zon-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"353\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
