(510, 255, 'content', '<strong><u>Rose water Soap</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Rose water helps in maintaining the pH balance of the skin and controls excess oil.</li>\r\n 	<li>It hydrates, cleans and regenerates tissues and gives a glowing skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Roses also have relaxing benefits that relax the body and reduce stress.</li>\r\n 	<li>For good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Rose Water, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E.\r\nProduct is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-256 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Rose-water-soap-compressed-11zon-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"353\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
