(162, 1, '2020-11-06 09:41:32', '2020-11-06 09:41:32', '<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Healthy and gentle soaps;</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\">handmade from fresh natural ingredients.</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"pale-pink\",\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-pale-pink-background-color has-text-color has-background has-medium-font-size\">Welcome to juniberrysoaps.com. Our soaps are carefully made with sensitive skin in mind, using natural ingredients. They are made with fresh pulp, puree, powders and extracts, coconut oil, olive and carrot oil, Vit E and essential oils. The soaps are mild, free of parabens, sulphates and preservatives. They have skin nourishing properties due to the infused natural extracts and other ingredients. Every product is given our personal touch. We make our soaps in small batches, with great care and thus ensure freshness. We hope you like and benefit from our products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#d0e4f4\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-medium-font-size\" style=\"background-color:#d0e4f4\">We encourage you to scroll down and look through each tab to find the soap that suits your skin type. We can also help you to select the right one for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#d0e4f4\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-medium-font-size\" style=\"background-color:#d0e4f4\">Should you have questions, please call or e-mail us.<