(201, 1, '2020-11-08 18:15:07', '2020-11-08 18:15:07', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong><u>INTRODUCTION</u></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">I had an extreme dry skin condition for almost ten years, which used to worsen at times. I tried several creams and medicines which only gave me temporary relief. I finally decided to try some natural medicine for my skin condition. After a lot of research, I came across the healing properties of common garden vegetables, leaves and herbs. I thought of trying handmade soaps infusing the fresh garden extracts. To my surprise it worked and my skin condition started improving from the very first week. My friends and family also started to try these handmade soaps and were amazed by the good results and glow they experienced on their skin.&nbsp; I developed and tried several different types of soaps based on the feedback and requirements given by the people who had started using my soap samples. It was encouraging to hear from them about how these soaps not only improved their skin, but also gave them relief from itching, dryness and other skin conditions. Some of the people who tried these soaps were diabetic patients who had extreme skin dryness. This was the beginning of Juniberry.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong><u>JUNIBERRY Handcrafted</u></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We take pride in our ingredients. Our soaps are handmade with natural and fresh products and are free of the harmful chemicals like sulphates and paraben. There is nothing in them but pure, simple fresh herbal extracts, Coconut oil, Carrot - Olive oil, essential oils, a minimum of fragrance oils and only natural colors. They are gentle on the skin, maintain the pH and retain moisture with the help of fresh, wholesome natural ingredients, thus giving a moisturizing and fresh feel. Our soaps are also tested time to time at the NABL and State Drug controller Dept. accredited Lab, to ascertain the product quality. We can even help you select the soap best suited for your skin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\"><strong><u>Outer beauty is generally a reflection of our inner health</u></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\"><strong><u>Eat well. exercise daily. hydrate often. sleep lots. Love your body.</u></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Â·&nbsp;Have a well balanced diet: include sufficient proteins, green leafy vegetables and salads in your diet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Â·&nbsp;Drink at least 2-3 litres of water daily, to keep yourself hydrated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Â·&nbsp;Go for walks or do some kind of exercise daily. This improves blood circulation in the body.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Â·&nbsp;Use a moisturizer and sunscreen regularly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Â·&nbsp;Wash your face thoroughly before bedtime. Get sufficient sleep.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Â·&nbsp;Maintain good personal hygiene.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '