(203, 1, '2020-11-08 18:22:06', '2020-11-08 18:22:06', '<div style=\"background-color: #ffd9e2; border: none;\">\r\n<h1 style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong>Product Description</strong></h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 40px;\"><strong><u>Goatmilk and Shea Butter Soap</u></strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gently cleanses the skin, without causing any dryness. It is very mild and safe to use for all skin conditions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides nutrients and anti oxidants to the skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Soothes sensitive and dry skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Goat milk contains an excellent emollient and is absorbed by the skin easily; it nourishes and moisturizes the skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Contains alpha-hydroxy acids which remove dead skin cells from the surface of your skin.</li>\r\n 	<li>This soap is best suited for extremely dry skin especially diabetic patients with itchiness on skin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">For good results apply the soap and lather for one to two minutes before washing off.\r\n<strong>Contains :</strong> Goatmilk, Shea butter, Coconut oil, Olive oil, Carrot oil, essential oils, Fragrance Oils and Vit. E. Product is free of Sulphate and Parabens.\r\n<strong>Suitable for:</strong> All skin types.\r\n<strong>Storage</strong>:Â  * Store in a cool and dry place after every use. Keep out of direct sunlight.\r\nPlace the bar on a soap dish which will allow proper drainage of water.\r\n<strong>Available in:</strong> 50gms / 100 gms</p>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-205 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/juniberry/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Goatmilk-Soap3-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"354\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>', 'GOATMILK AND SHEA BUTTER SOAP', '<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Enjoy the benefits of Shea butter combined with Goat Milk, making it a richer soap that is wonderful for people with dry, sensitive or even normal skin.</span>', 'p